A secret refuge
In an unknown and dangerous world, you can't survive alone. You must find the mansion Kiel spoke of, where you may find a safe haven.
#subobj 1
Get into town
The nearest bridge, straight into town, is guarded. Fortunately, the guards are not very attentive and there is a chance to slip through unnoticed.
#subobj 2
Avoid the encounter with the soldiers
The Portal area is patrolled by groups of warriors. It's best not to get in their way.
#subobj 3
Get to the Hideout
The Hideout Villa, as Kiel called him, is located in the north of the town. You'd better be on your guard along the way.